<br />

<br />
A few people told me since kiting or bard dot songs were nerfed they can't kite or anything at all and they said it makes leveling a pain..I was just wondering if thats true or not cause I've read a few guides here that seem to make sence.
<br />

<br />
Is it really all that hard to level a Bard up now? 
<br />
Is it still possible to kite around mobs?
<br />
I think I saw a guy kiting mobs at the Tables camp in Fire today but I could be wrong, Who knows.
<br />

<br />
Anyway, Was just wondering about that.
<br />

<br />
Thanks!</span></td>
