				<td colspan="2"><span>I have been playing EQ for 6 years and tryed every class atleast once and let me say I found my bard the easyest to level and most fun to play. Great mix of melee and magic. I am current level 56 and kite the werewolf camp in PoN for great AA and Loot ( EX: raw diamonds, diamonds and blue diamonds.) So I think it's safe to say YES we are easy to level, YES we can kite, we did lose the AE kite abitile to nerf, BUT can swarm kite once you get the needed songs and learn how and we can fear kite also. Bards are great for solo play and groups and as jake of all trades we can do so much it keeps it fun thur out the levels.</span></td>
